{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1082,"text":"I come to you today to speak of liars,"},{"time":5189,"text":"lawsuits"},{"time":6636,"text":"and laughter."},{"time":8910,"text":"The first time I heard\nabout Holocaust denial,"},{"time":12044,"text":"I laughed."},{"time":13970,"text":"Holocaust denial?"},{"time":16187,"text":"The Holocaust which has\nthe dubious distinction"},{"time":19641,"text":"of being the best-documented\ngenocide in the world?"},{"time":25046,"text":"Who could believe it didn't happen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28106,"text":"Think about it."},{"time":30257,"text":"For deniers to be right,"},{"time":32562,"text":"who would have to be wrong?"},{"time":35011,"text":"Well, first of all, the victims --"},{"time":37801,"text":"the survivors who have told us\ntheir harrowing stories."},{"time":43721,"text":"Who else would have to be wrong?"},{"time":46059,"text":"The bystanders."},{"time":48036,"text":"The people who lived in the myriads\nof towns and villages and cities"},{"time":52038,"text":"on the Eastern front,"},{"time":54034,"text":"who watched their neighbors\nbe rounded up --"},{"time":56500,"text":"men, women, children, young, old --"},{"time":59737,"text":"and be marched\nto the outskirts of the town"},{"time":62481,"text":"to be shot and left dead in ditches."},{"time":65985,"text":"Or the Poles,"},{"time":67339,"text":"who lived in towns and villages\naround the death camps,"},{"time":72044,"text":"who watched day after day"},{"time":74444,"text":"as the trains went in filled with people"},{"time":77210,"text":"and came out empty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79787,"text":"But above all, who would have to be wrong?"},{"time":84005,"text":"The perpetrators."},{"time":86112,"text":"The people who say, \"We did it."},{"time":89479,"text":"I did it.\""},{"time":91027,"text":"Now, maybe they add a caveat."},{"time":93200,"text":"They say, \"I didn't have a choice;\nI was forced to do it.\""},{"time":98104,"text":"But nonetheless, they say, \"I did it.\""},{"time":101938,"text":"Think about it."},{"time":103513,"text":"In not one war crimes trial\nsince the end of World War II"},{"time":109476,"text":"has a perpetrator of any nationality\never said, \"It didn't happen.\""},{"time":117078,"text":"Again, they may have said, \"I was forced,\"\nbut never that it didn't happen."},{"time":121684,"text":"Having thought that through,"},{"time":123182,"text":"I decided denial was not\ngoing to be on my agenda;"},{"time":127157,"text":"I had bigger things to worry about,\nto write about, to research,"},{"time":130889,"text":"and I moved on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132911,"text":"Fast-forward a little over a decade,"},{"time":135754,"text":"and two senior scholars --"},{"time":137590,"text":"two of the most prominent historians\nof the Holocaust --"},{"time":140772,"text":"approached me and said,"},{"time":142053,"text":"\"Deborah, let's have coffee."},{"time":143866,"text":"We have a research idea\nthat we think is perfect for you.\""},{"time":147487,"text":"Intrigued and flattered\nthat they came to me with an idea"},{"time":151344,"text":"and thought me worthy of it,"},{"time":152945,"text":"I asked, \"What is it?\""},{"time":155665,"text":"And they said, \"Holocaust denial.\""},{"time":159353,"text":"And for the second time, I laughed."},{"time":162336,"text":"Holocaust denial?"},{"time":164284,"text":"The Flat Earth folks?"},{"time":166294,"text":"The Elvis-is-alive people?"},{"time":168455,"text":"I should study them?"},{"time":171326,"text":"And these two guys said,"},{"time":172667,"text":"\"Yeah, we're intrigued."},{"time":175012,"text":"What are they about?"},{"time":176608,"text":"What's their objective?"},{"time":178382,"text":"How do they manage to get people\nto believe what they say?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":182756,"text":"So thinking, if they thought\nit was worthwhile,"},{"time":186308,"text":"I would take a momentary diversion --"},{"time":189706,"text":"maybe a year, maybe two,\nthree, maybe even four --"},{"time":192668,"text":"in academic terms, that's momentary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194937,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196103,"text":"We work very slowly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198514,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200110,"text":"And I would look at them."},{"time":201936,"text":"So I did."},{"time":203115,"text":"I did my research, and I came up\nwith a number of things,"},{"time":205978,"text":"two of which I'd like to share\nwith you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208595,"text":"One:"},{"time":209952,"text":"deniers are wolves in sheep's clothing."},{"time":215712,"text":"They are the same: Nazis, neo-Nazis --"},{"time":218701,"text":"you can decide whether you want\nto put a \"neo\" there or not."},{"time":222786,"text":"But when I looked at them,"},{"time":225143,"text":"I didn't see any SS-like uniforms,"},{"time":229893,"text":"swastika-like symbols on the wall,"},{"time":233068,"text":"Sieg Heil salutes --"},{"time":235149,"text":"none of that."},{"time":236717,"text":"What I found instead"},{"time":239611,"text":"were people parading\nas respectable academics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244916,"text":"What did they have?"},{"time":246161,"text":"They had an institute."},{"time":247883,"text":"An \"Institute for Historical Review.\""},{"time":252392,"text":"They had a journal -- a slick journal --"},{"time":254970,"text":"a \"Journal of Historical Review.\""},{"time":258398,"text":"One filled with papers --"},{"time":261128,"text":"footnote-laden papers."},{"time":263923,"text":"And they had a new name."},{"time":266500,"text":"Not neo-Nazis,"},{"time":268692,"text":"not anti-Semites --"},{"time":271206,"text":"revisionists."},{"time":272991,"text":"They said, \"We are revisionists."},{"time":275230,"text":"We are out to do one thing:"},{"time":277937,"text":"to revise mistakes in history.\""},{"time":282369,"text":"But all you had to do was go\none inch below the surface,"},{"time":287803,"text":"and what did you find there?"},{"time":289734,"text":"The same adulation of Hitler,"},{"time":292248,"text":"praise of the Third Reich,"},{"time":294147,"text":"anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice."},{"time":297904,"text":"This is what intrigued me."},{"time":300374,"text":"It was anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice,\nparading as rational discourse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308730,"text":"The other thing I found --"},{"time":310341,"text":"many of us have been taught to think\nthere are facts and there are opinions --"},{"time":314110,"text":"after studying deniers,"},{"time":315590,"text":"I think differently."},{"time":317438,"text":"There are facts,"},{"time":319110,"text":"there are opinions,"},{"time":320848,"text":"and there are lies."},{"time":323149,"text":"And what deniers want to do\nis take their lies,"},{"time":328565,"text":"dress them up as opinions --"},{"time":330221,"text":"maybe edgy opinions,"},{"time":332235,"text":"maybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions --"},{"time":334968,"text":"but then if they're opinions,"},{"time":336376,"text":"they should be part of the conversation."},{"time":338532,"text":"And then they encroach on the facts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343305,"text":"I published my work --"},{"time":344892,"text":"the book was published,"},{"time":346090,"text":"\"Denying the Holocaust: The Growing\nAssault on Truth and Memory,\""},{"time":349516,"text":"it came out in many different countries,"},{"time":351496,"text":"including here in Penguin UK,"},{"time":353680,"text":"and I was done with those folks\nand ready to move on."},{"time":358163,"text":"Then came the letter from Penguin UK."},{"time":362434,"text":"And for the third time, I laughed ..."},{"time":367088,"text":"mistakenly."},{"time":368972,"text":"I opened the letter,"},{"time":370726,"text":"and it informed me that David Irving\nwas bringing a libel suit against me"},{"time":376638,"text":"in the United Kingdom"},{"time":378259,"text":"for calling him a Holocaust denier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381953,"text":"David Irving suing me?"},{"time":383911,"text":"Who was David Irving?"},{"time":385139,"text":"David Irving was a writer\nof historical works,"},{"time":387770,"text":"most of them about World War II,"},{"time":389817,"text":"and virtually all of those works\ntook the position"},{"time":393060,"text":"that the Nazis were really not so bad,"},{"time":396662,"text":"and the Allies were really not so good."},{"time":399770,"text":"And the Jews, whatever happened to them,"},{"time":401899,"text":"they sort of deserved it."},{"time":404206,"text":"He knew the documents,"},{"time":405721,"text":"he knew the facts,"},{"time":407188,"text":"but he somehow twisted them\nto get this opinion."},{"time":411016,"text":"He hadn't always been a Holocaust denier,"},{"time":413552,"text":"but in the late '80s,"},{"time":415317,"text":"he embraced it with great vigor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419517,"text":"The reason I laughed also\nwas this was a man"},{"time":423446,"text":"who not only was a Holocaust denier,"},{"time":425404,"text":"but seemed quite proud of it."},{"time":427123,"text":"Here was a man -- and I quote --"},{"time":428771,"text":"who said, \"I'm going to sink\nthe battleship Auschwitz.\""},{"time":433345,"text":"Here was a man"},{"time":434541,"text":"who pointed to the number tattooed\non a survivor's arm and said,"},{"time":439716,"text":"\"How much money have you made"},{"time":441332,"text":"from having that number\ntattooed on your arm?\""},{"time":445549,"text":"Here was a man who said,"},{"time":447481,"text":"\"More people died in Senator Kennedy's car"},{"time":450461,"text":"at Chappaquiddick"},{"time":451797,"text":"than died in gas chambers at Auschwitz.\""},{"time":455135,"text":"That's an American reference,\nbut you can look it up."},{"time":459406,"text":"This was not a man who seemed\nat all ashamed or reticent"},{"time":462444,"text":"about being a Holocaust denier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465136,"text":"Now, lots of my academic\ncolleagues counseled me --"},{"time":468940,"text":"\"Eh, Deborah, just ignore it.\""},{"time":470870,"text":"When I explained you can't just\nignore a libel suit,"},{"time":474482,"text":"they said, \"Who's going to\nbelieve him anyway?\""},{"time":477783,"text":"But here was the problem:"},{"time":479887,"text":"British law put the onus,\nput the burden of proof on me"},{"time":485219,"text":"to prove the truth of what I said,"},{"time":487925,"text":"in contrast to as it would have\nbeen in the United States"},{"time":490712,"text":"and in many other countries:"},{"time":492240,"text":"on him to prove the falsehood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495921,"text":"What did that mean?"},{"time":497406,"text":"That meant if I didn't fight,"},{"time":500806,"text":"he would win by default."},{"time":503791,"text":"And if he won by default,"},{"time":505570,"text":"he could then legitimately say,"},{"time":508235,"text":"\"My David Irving version of the Holocaust\nis a legitimate version."},{"time":513595,"text":"Deborah Lipstadt was found\nto have libeled me"},{"time":515803,"text":"when she called me a Holocaust denier."},{"time":517774,"text":"Ipso facto, I, David Irving,\nam not a Holocaust denier.\""},{"time":522226,"text":"And what is that version?"},{"time":524431,"text":"There was no plan to murder the Jews,"},{"time":527451,"text":"there were no gas chambers,"},{"time":529527,"text":"there were no mass shootings,"},{"time":531407,"text":"Hitler had nothing to do\nwith any suffering that went on,"},{"time":534602,"text":"and the Jews have made this all up"},{"time":538431,"text":"to get money from Germany"},{"time":540853,"text":"and to get a state,"},{"time":542584,"text":"and they've done it with the aid\nand abettance of the Allies --"},{"time":545985,"text":"they've planted the documents\nand planted the evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550460,"text":"I couldn't let that stand"},{"time":552864,"text":"and ever face a survivor"},{"time":555823,"text":"or a child of survivors."},{"time":557822,"text":"I couldn't let that stand"},{"time":559998,"text":"and consider myself\na responsible historian."},{"time":565187,"text":"So we fought."},{"time":566956,"text":"And for those of you\nwho haven't seen \"Denial,\""},{"time":569262,"text":"spoiler alert:"},{"time":570445,"text":"we won."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571687,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573006,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":579988,"text":"The judge found David Irving"},{"time":584253,"text":"to be a liar,"},{"time":587608,"text":"a racist,"},{"time":588795,"text":"an anti-Semite."},{"time":590073,"text":"His view of history was tendentious,"},{"time":592457,"text":"he lied, he distorted --"},{"time":594407,"text":"and most importantly,"},{"time":597074,"text":"he did it deliberately."},{"time":599211,"text":"We showed a pattern,\nin over 25 different major instances."},{"time":603374,"text":"Not small things -- many of us\nin this audience write books,"},{"time":606508,"text":"are writing books;"},{"time":607717,"text":"we always make mistakes, that's why\nwe're glad to have second editions:"},{"time":611207,"text":"correct the mistakes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612417,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614634,"text":"But these always moved\nin the same direction:"},{"time":618618,"text":"blame the Jews,"},{"time":620853,"text":"exonerate the Nazis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623700,"text":"But how did we win?"},{"time":626196,"text":"What we did is follow his footnotes\nback to his sources."},{"time":632190,"text":"And what did we find?"},{"time":633997,"text":"Not in most cases,"},{"time":635500,"text":"and not in the preponderance of cases,"},{"time":637492,"text":"but in every single instance where\nhe made some reference to the Holocaust,"},{"time":641827,"text":"that his supposed evidence was distorted,"},{"time":646093,"text":"half-truth,"},{"time":647537,"text":"date-changed,"},{"time":648895,"text":"sequence-changed,"},{"time":651106,"text":"someone put at a meeting who wasn't there."},{"time":653254,"text":"In other words,\nhe didn't have the evidence."},{"time":656039,"text":"His evidence didn't prove it."},{"time":658172,"text":"We didn't prove what happened."},{"time":661628,"text":"We proved that what he said happened --"},{"time":664151,"text":"and by extension, all deniers,\nbecause he either quotes them"},{"time":667035,"text":"or they get their arguments from him --"},{"time":669530,"text":"is not true."},{"time":670800,"text":"What they claim --"},{"time":672013,"text":"they don't have the evidence to prove it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676609,"text":"So why is my story\nmore than just the story"},{"time":681377,"text":"of a quirky, long,\nsix-year, difficult lawsuit,"},{"time":685208,"text":"an American professor\nbeing dragged into a courtroom"},{"time":690221,"text":"by a man that the court\ndeclared in its judgment"},{"time":693289,"text":"was a neo-Nazi polemicist?"},{"time":695563,"text":"What message does it have?"},{"time":697800,"text":"I think in the context\nof the question of truth,"},{"time":700797,"text":"it has a very significant message."},{"time":703283,"text":"Because today,"},{"time":705092,"text":"as we well know,"},{"time":706782,"text":"truth and facts are under assault."},{"time":711702,"text":"Social media, for all\nthe gifts it has given us,"},{"time":714978,"text":"has also allowed the difference\nbetween facts -- established facts --"},{"time":720583,"text":"and lies"},{"time":722364,"text":"to be flattened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724990,"text":"Third of all:"},{"time":726524,"text":"extremism."},{"time":728987,"text":"You may not see Ku Klux Klan robes,"},{"time":732588,"text":"you may not see burning crosses,"},{"time":734683,"text":"you may not even hear outright\nwhite supremacist language."},{"time":739026,"text":"It may go by names: \"alt-right,\"\n\"National Front\" -- pick your names."},{"time":743956,"text":"But underneath, it's that same extremism\nthat I found in Holocaust denial"},{"time":749815,"text":"parading as rational discourse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755134,"text":"We live in an age\nwhere truth is on the defensive."},{"time":760375,"text":"I'm reminded of a New Yorker cartoon."},{"time":762883,"text":"A quiz show recently appeared\nin \"The New Yorker\""},{"time":765427,"text":"where the host of the quiz show\nis saying to one of the contestants,"},{"time":768673,"text":"\"Yes, ma'am, you had the right answer."},{"time":771006,"text":"But your opponent yelled\nmore loudly than you did,"},{"time":773523,"text":"so he gets the point.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":776228,"text":"What can we do?"},{"time":778557,"text":"First of all,"},{"time":779958,"text":"we cannot be beguiled\nby rational appearances."},{"time":785413,"text":"We've got to look underneath,"},{"time":787206,"text":"and we will find there the extremism."},{"time":790991,"text":"Second of all,"},{"time":793001,"text":"we must understand\nthat truth is not relative."},{"time":801137,"text":"Number three,"},{"time":802625,"text":"we must go on the offensive,"},{"time":806338,"text":"not the defensive."},{"time":808676,"text":"When someone makes an outrageous claim,"},{"time":811307,"text":"even though they may hold\none of the highest offices in the land,"},{"time":814835,"text":"if not the world --"},{"time":816870,"text":"we must say to them,"},{"time":818404,"text":"\"Where's the proof?"},{"time":820394,"text":"Where's the evidence?\""},{"time":822555,"text":"We must hold their feet to the fire."},{"time":825506,"text":"We must not treat it as if their lies\nare the same as the facts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831395,"text":"And as I said earlier,\ntruth is not relative."},{"time":834959,"text":"Many of us have grown up\nin the world of the academy"},{"time":837839,"text":"and enlightened liberal thought,"},{"time":839604,"text":"where we're taught\neverything is open to debate."},{"time":843164,"text":"But that's not the case."},{"time":845202,"text":"There are certain things that are true."},{"time":849192,"text":"There are indisputable facts --"},{"time":852236,"text":"objective truths."},{"time":854519,"text":"Galileo taught it to us centuries ago."},{"time":859360,"text":"Even after being forced\nto recant by the Vatican"},{"time":864051,"text":"that the Earth moved around the Sun,"},{"time":866648,"text":"he came out,"},{"time":867826,"text":"and what is he reported to have said?"},{"time":870160,"text":"\"And yet, it still moves.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":875342,"text":"The Earth is not flat."},{"time":878206,"text":"The climate is changing."},{"time":881387,"text":"Elvis is not alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883679,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":885238,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887578,"text":"And most importantly,"},{"time":889903,"text":"truth and fact are under assault."},{"time":895289,"text":"The job ahead of us,"},{"time":896923,"text":"the task ahead of us,"},{"time":898150,"text":"the challenge ahead of us"},{"time":899768,"text":"is great."},{"time":901747,"text":"The time to fight is short."},{"time":905241,"text":"We must act now."},{"time":908929,"text":"Later will be too late."}]},{"cues":[{"time":912198,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913484,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}